1
00:00:06,340 --> 00:00:09,940
=The Queen System=
=Episode 13=

2
00:00:13,630 --> 00:00:15,120
I'm Ye Chang'an and I'm back.

3
00:00:15,950 --> 00:00:17,040
Emperor Jingxuan,

4
00:00:17,400 --> 00:00:18,360
I'll make you pay

5
00:00:19,360 --> 00:00:21,190
for what you owed me.

6
00:00:44,080 --> 00:00:44,630
(Wu,)

7
00:00:46,310 --> 00:00:48,160
(I also want to go
to the modern world with you.)

8
00:00:49,630 --> 00:00:51,630
(But the war against the Luo
isn't over yet.)

9
00:00:52,480 --> 00:00:53,590
(As the Emperor,)

10
00:00:54,360 --> 00:00:56,120
(I can't disregard my people.)

11
00:00:56,870 --> 00:00:58,040
(What do you think, Wu?)

12
00:00:58,870 --> 00:01:00,190
(To you, Your Majesty,)

13
00:01:00,760 --> 00:01:02,480
(your state and people matter most.)

14
00:01:03,360 --> 00:01:04,910
(But to me,)

15
00:01:06,080 --> 00:01:06,870
(you are)

16
00:01:07,760 --> 00:01:08,910
(the most important.)

17
00:01:10,120 --> 00:01:11,720
Why not stay for tonight, Your Majesty?

18
00:01:22,400 --> 00:01:23,480
What are you burning?

19
00:01:24,630 --> 00:01:25,630
Nothing.

20
00:01:26,510 --> 00:01:27,680
It's still early.

21
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:29,080
Why did you come here?

22
00:01:29,480 --> 00:01:30,360
Is it because you missed me?

23
00:01:31,270 --> 00:01:31,910
Where's His Majesty?

24
00:01:32,000 --> 00:01:32,870
I'm looking for him.

25
00:01:33,310 --> 00:01:35,120
He left after he got up.

26
00:01:36,040 --> 00:01:37,040
Didn't you say

27
00:01:37,230 --> 00:01:39,310
that His Majesty wasn't yours alone

28
00:01:39,590 --> 00:01:40,830
and he should sleep
with all his concubines?

29
00:01:41,550 --> 00:01:42,310
Bai Qingqing,

30
00:01:43,510 --> 00:01:44,120
you've changed

31
00:01:44,120 --> 00:01:46,040
and I can hardly recognize you.

32
00:01:46,950 --> 00:01:48,440
I'm not Bai Qingqing at all.

33
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:50,190
I've had enough of you.

34
00:01:50,510 --> 00:01:52,120
All emperors are inconstant in love.

35
00:01:52,480 --> 00:01:53,440
I'm Ye Chang'an

36
00:01:53,680 --> 00:01:54,950
and I'm back for revenge.

37
00:01:57,190 --> 00:01:57,760
Your Majesty,

38
00:01:57,910 --> 00:01:58,590
you heard her, right?

39
00:01:58,680 --> 00:01:59,760
She said she was Ye Chang'an.

40
00:02:00,550 --> 00:02:01,440
Nonsense.

41
00:02:01,680 --> 00:02:02,870
Ye Chang'an died a long time ago.

42
00:02:03,510 --> 00:02:05,000
No one shall bring her up again.

43
00:02:07,160 --> 00:02:08,910
Very well, hope you can stay alive.

44
00:02:10,120 --> 00:02:10,830
Your Majesty,

45
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:12,440
don't be angry.

46
00:02:12,910 --> 00:02:15,400
You should focus more on our state.

47
00:02:15,510 --> 00:02:16,680
You make sense, Qingqing.

48
00:02:17,230 --> 00:02:18,080
Without you,

49
00:02:18,400 --> 00:02:19,480
the Luo Army

50
00:02:19,680 --> 00:02:21,120
wouldn't have retreated.

51
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:23,550
You're quite possessed.

52
00:02:24,040 --> 00:02:25,510
For your people?

53
00:02:25,720 --> 00:02:27,040
For the beautiful girl, obviously.

54
00:02:27,550 --> 00:02:28,230
Mu Wu!

55
00:02:31,380 --> 00:02:33,100
(Emperor Jingxuan, Ye Chang'an)

56
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:35,040
♪I miss you a lot♪

57
00:02:35,120 --> 00:02:37,720
♪But I pretend I don't♪

58
00:02:38,230 --> 00:02:41,950
♪We met hurriedly
and you stole my heart♪

59
00:02:42,480 --> 00:02:44,000
♪The pledges we've made♪

60
00:02:44,160 --> 00:02:46,590
♪Shall I believe them♪

61
00:02:46,950 --> 00:02:50,760
♪In your heart I want to be♪

62
00:02:51,160 --> 00:02:54,950
♪The one and only♪

63
